  "description": "Giant Digger is a steel linear synchronous motor (LSM) launched roller coaster located in Lotte World Adventure Busan, South Korea, built by Mack Rides.  Lotte World Adventure Busan began construction on May 2019, and Giant Digger was supposed to open alongside the park in May 2021.  However, the coaster was delayed 3 months until August 2021, then further delayed until March 2022 due to delays in manufacturing and safety testing as well as COVID-19 pandemic related risks.",
